  _aiDescription: Tanky unit with huge HP amount and solid damage, but slow movement and very slow attack speed. ALWAYS should have 1 amount under slot settings.  It's related to cell settings only. However, troll can be used multiple times in different slots in the same wave. It's possible to have 2, 3, or 4 trolls under same wave
